Package org.semanticweb.rulewerk.core.model.api

Interface Variable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity, Term
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExistentialVariable, UniversalVariable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExistentialVariableImpl, UniversalVariableImpl
    public interface Variable
extends Term
    Interface for variables, i.e., terms of type TermType.UNIVERSAL_VARIABLE and TermType.EXISTENTIAL_VARIABLE. Variables are terms that can be quantified to create formulas that refer to some or all values of the domain.
